就像增加限制一样。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 08:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-sanction-hit-tech-industry-puzzles-over-impact-trump-harris-presidencies-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金庆祝活动引发印度购买热潮，但成交量滞后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-festivities-trigger-buying-spree-india-volumes-lag-2024-11-01/</link><description>印度的黄金需求本周因节日采购而猛增，但由于价格创历史新高，成交量低于平时。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 07:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-festivities-trigger-buying-spree-india-volumes-lag-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：值得纪念的十一月......</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-01/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 05:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国转向美国农产品进口有助于抵御贸易战风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-pivot-us-farm-imports-bolsters-it-against-trade-war-risks-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国自2018年以来努力改变粮食进口来源，这使得如果美国总统大选后中美贸易摩擦爆发，中国更有能力对美国农产品征收针锋相对的关税，同时减少对中国粮食安全的损害。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 04:29:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-pivot-us-farm-imports-bolsters-it-against-trade-war-risks-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲工厂活动停滞不前，削弱了中国的反弹势头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-asias-factory-activity-stagnates-taking-shine-off-rebound-china-2024-11-01/</link><description>对于准备应对美中贸易紧张局势可能升级的政策制定者来说，该数据是一个令人沮丧的信号。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 03:43:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-asias-factory-activity-stagnates-taking-shine-off-rebound-china-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国谴责对中国著名人权捍卫者的判刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-condemns-sentencing-prominent-chinese-human-rights-defenders-2024-11-01/</link><description>美国周五谴责中国著名人权律师余文生及其妻子徐艳的“不公正监禁”，中国一家法院本周分别判处他们三年和一年零九个月的刑期。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 03:20:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-condemns-sentencing-prominent-chinese-human-rights-defenders-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国研究人员在梅塔骆驼背上开发军事用途人工智能模型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-researchers-develop-ai-model-military-use-back-metas-llama-2024-11-01/</link><description>根据三篇学术论文和分析师的说法，与中国人民解放军有联系的中国顶级研究机构已使用 Meta 公开的 Llama 模型来开发一种用于潜在军事应用的人工智能工具。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 02:38:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-researchers-develop-ai-model-military-use-back-metas-llama-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>台风“康瑞”残骸掠过中国海岸后，台湾进行了清理工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/taiwan-clears-up-remnant-typhoon-kong-rey-brushes-chinese-coast-2024-11-01/</link><description>周五，强大的台风“康瑞”席卷台湾，造成两人死亡，交通运输中断，风暴余波掠过中国海岸后，台湾天气晴朗，办公楼和金融市场重新开放。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 02:35:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/taiwan-clears-up-remnant-typhoon-kong-rey-brushes-chinese-coast-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国就业数据的临近，市场以谨慎的态度开始了重要的一个月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-01/</link><description>市场谨慎地开始了这可能是重要的一个月，在美国就业数据公布之前，股市稳定，国债收益率接近四个月高点，本周预算公布后英国政府债券的波动加剧了紧张感。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 02:12:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国海军在南海举行首次双机编队演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-pla-navy-perform-first-dual-aircraft-formation-exercise-south-china-sea-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国海军表示，辽宁舰和山东舰首次在南海进行双航母编队演习，此举为中国海军执行更加多样化和复杂的任务奠定了基础。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 02:04:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-pla-navy-perform-first-dual-aircraft-formation-exercise-south-china-sea-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国10月工厂活动恢复扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-oct-factory-activity-returns-expansion-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-11-01/</link><description>周五的一项私营部门调查显示，随着新订单的扩大导致产量增长回升，中国制造业活动在 10 月份恢复增长，这表明该行业在最后一个季度初有所改善。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 01:49:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-oct-factory-activity-returns-expansion-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织警告称，贸易紧张局势和中国经济增长疲软将给亚洲经济带来风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/imf-warns-risks-asias-economy-trade-tensions-soft-china-growth-bite-2024-11-01/</link><description>国际货币基金组织敦促北京采取措施，实现更多由需求驱动的经济复苏。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 01:34:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/imf-warns-risks-asias-economy-trade-tensions-soft-china-growth-bite-2024-11-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>